# Instagram engagement bot — local-only state & secrets. NEVER commit these.
# The session cookie is a live login credential; the state files are per-account
# runtime data that only exists on the VPS.

# Login cookie (Playwright storage_state) — treat as a password.
session.json

# Runtime state (rebuilt on the VPS, account-specific).
engaged.json
replied.json
follows.json
summaries.log
optimization.log

# Logs
logs/

# Secrets (this bot also reads the repo-root .env, but ignore any local copy).
.env
